WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.460 --> 00:00:03.086
[Narrator] A mathematical message

2
00:00:03.253 --> 00:00:06.173
encoded on opposite sides of the globe.

3
00:00:06.340 --> 00:00:08.342
Complex crop circles

4
00:00:08.550 --> 00:00:11.678
designed to transmit sound frequencies.

5
00:00:11.803 --> 00:00:13.972
And colossal figures

6
00:00:14.139 --> 00:00:17.643
which can only be seen from the sky.

7
