00:40:14.996 --> 00:40:16.831
they realized that maybe it was possible

807
00:40:16.998 --> 00:40:18.499
that it came from aliens.

808
00:40:18.708 --> 00:40:22.086
One reason was that the message was so perfect.

809
00:40:22.253 --> 00:40:25.590
How likely is it that some crop circle impostor

810
00:40:25.757 --> 00:40:28.801
could they have duplicated that message in a crop circle?

811
00:40:28.927 --> 00:40:30.803
Crop circles are very important

812
00:40:30.929 --> 00:40:33.681
the potential way in which an extraterrestrial intelligence

813
00:40:33.806 --> 00:40:35.475
could use to communicate with us.

814
00:40:35.642 --> 00:40:37.018
They are very public.

815
00:40:37.226 --> 00:40:39.896
and they aroused the curiosity of humanity.

816
00:40:43.274 --> 00:40:47.028
It was the so-called "Arecibo response" sent to Earth

817
00:40:47.195 --> 00:40:49.614
by an extraterrestrial civilization?

818
00:40:49.781 --> 00:40:51.616
It is completely possible.

819
00:40:51.783 --> 00:40:54.243
But maybe the better question is.

820
00:40:54.410 --> 00:40:57.830
Are we prepared to receive the information contained?

821
00:40:57.997 --> 00:41:00.875
in these hidden messages that are all around us?

822
00:41:02.335 --> 00:41:03.795
One thing is clear:

823
00:41:03.962 --> 00:41:07.507
whether they are massive geoglyphs...

824
00:41:07.674 --> 00:41:10.218
imposing monoliths...

825
00:41:10.426 --> 00:41:13.638
or elaborate circles in fields...

826
00:41:13.805 --> 00:41:16.933
once these extraordinary sites are decoded.

827
00:41:17.100 --> 00:41:20.937
we might be one step closer to finding out the truth

828
00:41:21.145 --> 00:41:24.399
from our alien past.

829
